note right of Browser
  **Frontend stack:**
  - Next.js: SSR/SSG、App Router
  - React 19: UI runtime
  - TypeScript: type safety
  - Emotion: Emotion CSS-in-JS in editor
  - Tailwind CSS: Tailwind tokens, shadcn, with Emotion
  - Zustand: state
  - react-i18next: i18n
  - Workspace packages: components, binding, layout, performance, schema
  - Local Storage: browser storage
  - AI generator: multi-provider (incl. Ollama)
end note

note right of AppServer
  **Backend (this repo):**
  - FastAPI: REST API
  - Python + Pydantic: validation & models
  - Uvicorn: ASGI host
end note

note right of PostgreSQL
  **Data storage:**
  - PostgreSQL: relational
  - Redis: cache & sessions
  - Object storage: & media (S3)
  - Local Storage: browser (prefs & temp)
end note

note right of AWSIntegration
  **AWS:**
  - S3: object storage
  - CloudFormation: IaC
  - Lambda: Lambda
  - API Gateway: API gateway
  - CloudFront: CDN
  - IAM: IAM
end note

note right of CollaborationPackage
  **Collaboration package:**
  - WebSocket: WS connections
  - Realtime sync: multi-user sync
  - Conflicts: conflict handling
end note

note right of CloudPlatform
  **Deployment:**
  - Microservices
  - Horizontal scale
  - Load balance
  - HA
end note

